East Texas Preferred Properties, LLC - Kilgore

data.description: Spacious home in the heart of Kilgore just minutes from shopping, dining, and entertainment. Beyond the front entry is a large open family room and wood-burning fireplace. The Eat-in kitchen is large enough to have a small island. Enormous master suite. The bathroom features a double vanity, jetted soaking tub, and separate walk-in closets. The backyard is fenced and is perfect for kids and pets to run and play. Hurry to take a look!
